| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1068 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7eb93de0-3ae2-51e8-9b26-6f5c112b795b"
